caption: One if my favorites ramen spots

Excellent ramen, and service.  We have trouble finding good ramen, even in the bigger cities.  Here, in this little shop, you will become a lover of ramen, if you weren't already, and will be reminded that when food comes first, the elaborateness of the venue and location become meaningless.

We are visiting from the Bay Area and my son loves ramen.  Anywhere we go, we have to find ramen.  We tried this place out and loved all of the food!  The tonkatsu ramen is delicious, the fried chicken is so flavorful, edamame was so good!  Everything we ordered was great!   Would definitely come back!
There is the best ramen in San Diego,  I will recomend tgis place for everyone
Great food.
